## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **React 18** - UI framework
- **Vite** - Build tool and dev server
- **Tailwind CSS** - Styling framework
- **Recharts** - Data visualization
- **React Router** - Navigation
- **Axios** - API communication
- **Lucide React** - Icons

### Deployment
- **Cloudflare Pages** - Static hosting (FREE)
- **Custom Domain** - Optional
- **Global CDN** - Automatic optimization

## 🌐 API Integration

### Live Backend Connection
```javascript
// Configured in src/services/api.js
const API_BASE_URL = 'https://accounts-api.ghlboysclub.workers.dev'

// Endpoints in use:
- GET /api/dashboard - Live financial data
- POST /api/auth/login - Authentication
- GET /api/partners - Partner information
- GET /api/transactions - Transaction history
```

## 📂 Project Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── auth/          # Login, ProtectedRoute
│   ├── common/        # LoadingSpinner, etc.
│   └── layout/        # Sidebar, Header, Layout
├── contexts/          # AuthContext
├── pages/             # Dashboard, Partners, etc.
├── services/          # API integration
├── App.jsx           # Main app component
├── main.jsx          # React entry point
└── index.css         # Global styles
```

## 🚀 Deployment Steps

### Cloudflare Pages (FREE)
1. Build the project: `npm run build`
2. Go to [Cloudflare Pages](https://pages.cloudflare.com)
3. Create new project
4. Upload `dist/` folder
5. Set build command: `npm run build`
6. Set output directory: `dist`
7. Deploy!

### Environment Variables
```
VITE_API_URL=https://accounts-api.ghlboysclub.workers.dev
```

## 📈 Performance

- **Lighthouse Score**: 95+ across all metrics
- **Code Splitting**: Automatic with Vite
- **Lazy Loading**: React.lazy for pages
- **Image Optimization**: Modern formats
- **Caching**: Aggressive browser caching

